  <brief_title>A Phase 4 Study of Imrecoxib in Treatment of Knee Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter，Open-label Phase Ⅳ Trial of Imrecoxib in Treatment of Knee Osteoarthritis</official_title>
